       <HR>
       <FONT size="+1"> Intracellular flush solution for preserving organs
</FONT><BR>
       <BR><CENTER><b>Abstract</b></CENTER>
       <p>The present invention is directed to a new hypersomotic intracellular flush
     and storage solution for preserving an organ for transplantation. In
     addition, the present invention is directed to a method for preserving an
     organ to be transplanted by using the flush solution of the invention.
     Among the components of the solution are various physiologic salts,
     mannitol, adenosine, allopurinol and <B><I>verapamil</I></B>.
</p>
       <HR>
